Title: Artisan's Supply: Jeweler's Specs
Description:
Are you looking for work, jewelcrafter? The Artisan's Consortium asked me to craft some spectacles for their customers. 

Me! Like I have time for this.

You can do it, yeah?
ObjectivesText: Deliver Sundered Onyx Loupes to Haephesta at the Ruby Lifeshrine.
